# CLIP ChangeLog for clip-layout/baselayout-core-udatepriv

*baselayout-core-updatepriv-1.0.1-r9 (05 Mar 2012)

  05 Mar 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-updatepriv-1.0.1-r9.ebuild, -baselayout-core-updatepriv-1.0.1-r8.ebuild:
  Add pts/ptmx to support PID namespace in UPDATE.

  25 May 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  baselayout-core-updatepriv-1.0.1-r8.ebuild:
  Use numeric value for cron group to avoid inconsistencies.

